s to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth was born about 1438, in Yate, Gloucestershire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 daughter with John Belsire. She died after 1459."},"et":{"Abt 1438–after 1459":"umbes 1438–pärast 1459","1434–1459":"1434–1459","1460–1515":"1460–1515","1438–1459":"1438–1459","1459":"1459","after 1459":"pärast 1459","1434":"1434","1460":"1460","Abt 1438":"umbes 1438","1438":"1438","1515":"1515","Yate, South Gloucestershire district, Gloucestershire, England, United Kingdom":"Yate, Gloucestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1438–after 1459":"noin 1438–1459 jälkeen","1434–1459":"1434–1459","1460–1515":"1460–1515","1438–1459":"1438–1459","1459":"1459","after 1459":"1459 jälkeen","1434":"1434","1460":"1460","Abt 1438":"noin 1438","1438":"1438","1515":"1515","Yate, South Gloucestershire district, Gloucestershire, England, United Kingdom":"Yate, Gloucestershire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1438–after 1459":"environ 1438–après 1459","1434–1459":"1434–1459","1460–1515":"1460–1515","1438–1459":"1438–1459","1459":"1459","after 1459":"après 1459","1434":"1434","1460":"1460","Abt 1438":"environ 1438","1438":"1438","1515":"1515","Yate, South Gloucestershire district, Gloucestershire, England, United Kingdom":"Yate, Gloucestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth est née environ 1438, à Yate, Gloucestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec John Belsire. Elle est décédée après 1459."},"de":{"Abt 1438–after 1459":"um 1438–nach 1459","1434–1459":"1434–1459","1460–1515":"1460–1515","1438–1459":"1438–1459","1459":"1459","after 1459":"nach 1459","1434":"1434","1460":"1460","Abt 1438":"um 1438","1438":"1438","1515":"1515","Yate, South Gloucestershire district, Gloucestershire, England, United Kingdom":"Yate, Gloucestershire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth wurde um 1438 in Yate, Gloucestershire, 